    "144865909": {
      "title": "International cooperation in a fractured global order",
      "abstract": "Abstract This article takes a fresh look at the context for international cooperation in science and technology. It sketches out some key changes that have taken place in the international scene over the last few years, speculates about what is likely to happen during the next decade, and derives some implications for international cooperation in science and technology."
